2:
Day after day speech pours out;
\q night after night it reveals knowledge.
\q

6:
The sun rises from the one horizon
\q and crosses the sky to the other;
\q nothing escapes its heat.

7:
The law of Yahweh is perfect, restoring the soul;
\q the testimony of Yahweh is reliable, making the simple wise.
\q

9:
The fear of Yahweh is pure, enduring forever;
\q the righteous decrees of Yahweh are true and altogether right!
\q

11:
Yes, by them your servant is warned;
\q in obeying them there is great reward.
\q
